::Killfest/Greven/EndBringer::

Killfest nods, taking a jetpack. Greven and EndBringer enter behind 
him, also taking jetpacks.

"Me, Greven, and EndBringer will attack them at the Maximal base. 
Scyther, Incarcinator, and Pinsir will attack at Hell Beast's base."

He motions form Greven and EndBringer to follow, heading out of the 
base and toward the surface.
